, male genitalia, a tergite viii b tegmen, dorsal view c tegmen, lateral view d parameres, dorsal view e parameres, ventral view f median lobe, ventral view g sclerities in endophallus. Scale bar 0.5 mm.
</paragraph>
</caption>
